(17246, 1, 0, 'It looks like it be succulent pork ribs basted with its own delectable juices and a side o'' Captain Sander''s Secret Sauce - fer dippin''.', 12, 7, 100, 1, 0, 0, '"Cookie" McWeaksauce', 13700),
